Package ure.areas

Class UCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • ure.areas.UCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UContainer
    public class UCell
extends java.lang.Object
implements UContainer
    UCell represents a single XY cell of an area. These are created on area creation along with a terrain. They have no type and should not need to be subclassed, however, a custom UCell class can be given to Area on creation. TODO: actually implement what I just said in Area
